  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Steamed Ham Sandwich</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/32px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p>The <b>Steamed Ham Sandwich</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">Item</a> exclusive to the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Hamlet</a></i> DLC.\n</p><p>It requires 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Foliage\" title=\"Foliage\">Foliage</a>, 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meat\" title=\"Meat\">Meat</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cooked_Meat\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cooked Meat\">Cooked Meat</a>, plus a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot#Food_values\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Vegetable value</a> of 1.0 or higher. It takes 40 seconds to cook and 6 days to spoil. When consumed, it restores 40 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Health\" title=\"Health\"><img alt=\"Health Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Health_Icon.png/20px-Health_Icon.png?1ec0e6\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a>, 37.5 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hunger\" title=\"Hunger\"><img alt=\"Hunger Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hunger_Icon.png/20px-Hunger_Icon.png?9d0486\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a> and 15 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sanity\" title=\"Sanity\"><img alt=\"Sanity Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Sanity_Icon.png/20px-Sanity_Icon.png?eae728\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a>.\n</p><p>Using <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twigs</a> as filler will yield <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kabobs\" title=\"Kabobs\">Kabobs</a> 50 percent of the time. <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake_Soup\" title=\"Mandrake Soup\">Mandrake Soup</a> has higher <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot#Priority\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Priority</a>, and will be the result if a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\">Mandrake</a> is used as filler. Similarly, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spicy_Chili\" title=\"Spicy Chili\">Spicy Chili</a> will be the result if any more <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meat</a> is added, and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Asparagus_Soup\" title=\"Asparagus Soup\">Asparagus Soup</a> will be given if <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Asparagus\" title=\"Asparagus\">Asparagus</a> is used as filler.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prerequisites\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Foliage\" title=\"Foliage\"><img alt=\"Foliage.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Foliage.png?69c04c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meat\" title=\"Meat\"><img alt=\"Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meat.png?ff3bf2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cooked_Meat\" title=\"Cooked Meat\"><img alt=\"Cooked Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cooked_Meat.png?31f10a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Vegetables Crock Pot(No Mandrake).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Vegetables_Crock_Pot%28No_Mandrake%29.png?2138af\" width=\"466\" height=\"130\"></a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meat\" title=\"Meat\"><img alt=\"Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meat.png?ff3bf2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Foliage\" title=\"Foliage\"><img alt=\"Foliage.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Foliage.png?69c04c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Veggie.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Veggie.png?80149d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich\" title=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich\"><img alt=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich.png?5abbe4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cooked_Meat\" title=\"Cooked Meat\"><img alt=\"Cooked Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cooked_Meat.png?31f10a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Foliage\" title=\"Foliage\"><img alt=\"Foliage.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Foliage.png?69c04c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Veggie.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Veggie.png?80149d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich\" title=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich\"><img alt=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich.png?5abbe4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meat\" title=\"Meat\"><img alt=\"Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meat.png?ff3bf2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Foliage\" title=\"Foliage\"><img alt=\"Foliage.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Foliage.png?69c04c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggplant\" title=\"Eggplant\"><img alt=\"Eggplant.png\" src=\"http