wiki/Gummy_Slug\" title=\"Gummy Slug\"><img alt=\"Gummy Slug.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Gummy_Slug.png?17e177\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich\" title=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich\"><img alt=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich.png?5abbe4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meat\" title=\"Meat\"><img alt=\"Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meat.png?ff3bf2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Foliage\" title=\"Foliage\"><img alt=\"Foliage.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Foliage.png?69c04c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Corn\" title=\"Corn\"><img alt=\"Corn.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Corn.png?569259\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Durian\" title=\"Durian\"><img alt=\"Durian.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Durian.png?569b17\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich\" title=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich\"><img alt=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich.png?5abbe4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cooked_Meat\" title=\"Cooked Meat\"><img alt=\"Cooked Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cooked_Meat.png?31f10a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Foliage\" title=\"Foliage\"><img alt=\"Foliage.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Foliage.png?69c04c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Green_Cap\" title=\"Green Cap\"><img alt=\"Green Cap.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Green_Cap.png?cd2f87\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich\" title=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich\"><img alt=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich.png?5abbe4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cooked_Meat\" title=\"Cooked Meat\"><img alt=\"Cooked Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cooked_Meat.png?31f10a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Foliage\" title=\"Foliage\"><img alt=\"Foliage.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Foliage.png?69c04c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Corn\" title=\"Corn\"><img alt=\"Corn.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Corn.png?569259\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich\" title=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich\"><img alt=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich.png?5abbe4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>50% chance to make <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kabobs\" title=\"Kabobs\">Kabobs</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<div class=\"floatright\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Steamed_Ham_Sandwich_(Pig_Fiesta).png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Steamed Ham Sandwich (Pig Fiesta).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich_%28Pig_Fiesta%29.png?54cc41\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div>\n<ul><li>During the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Fiesta\" title=\"Pig Fiesta\">Pig Fiesta</a> event, Steamed Ham Sandwich takes on a more festive appearance.</li>\n<li>The Steamed Ham Sandwich is a reference to a scene from an episode of <i><a href=\"https://community.fandom.com/c:Simpsons\" class=\"extiw external\" title=\"w:c:Simpsons\">The Simpsons</a></i> titled &quot;22 Short Films about Springfield&quot;, where the character Principal Skinner buys hamburgers and calls them steamed hams. The scene has become a popular meme and every examination line for it references it in some way.</li>\n<li>Since Foliage is non-renewable in <i>Hamlet</i>, only a limited number of Steamed Ham Sandwiches can be made without using the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wooden_Thing\" title=\"Wooden Thing\">Teleportato</a> or a connected <i>Reign of Giants</i> world.</li></ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Steamed_Ham_Sandwich#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
