  "plainText": "Exclusive to:\nSteamed Ham Sandwich\nNormal\nPig Fiesta\nFood Info\n37.5\n40\n15\nMeat\nObject Info\n6 days\nCan be Burned\n40\nCooking Info\nx1 x1 x1 x1\nx1 x1 x1 x1\n40 sec\n5\nMiscellaneous\n\"steamedhamsandwich\"\n“Science says it's a hamburger.”\n–Wilson\n“It's a ham sandwich.”\n–Willow\n“Is mouthwatering hamburgers.”\n–Wolfgang\n“Old family recipe.”\n–Wendy\n“AN UNFORGETTABLE LUNCHEON”\n–WX-78\n“I am prepared for an unforgettable luncheon.”\n–Wickerbottom\n“Mouth watering hamburgers.”\n–Woodie\n“They're obviously grilled.”\n–Maxwell\n“Delightfully devilish.”\n–Wagstaff\n“'Tis öbviöusly grilled!”\n–Wigfrid\n“These are just hamburgers.”\n–Webber\n“It's fast food.”\n–Walani\n“Tastes like fast food.”\n–Warly\n“'tis a'unforgettable luncheon.”\n–Woodlegs\n“WILBA THOUGHT SHE WAS'T HAVING STEAMED CLAMS”\n–Wilba\n“Egads!”\n–Wormwood\n“I thought I was having steamed clams.”\n–Wheeler\nThe Steamed Ham Sandwich is a Crock Pot Food Item exclusive to the Hamlet DLC.\nIt requires 1 Foliage, 1 Meat or Cooked Meat, plus a Vegetable value of 1.0 or higher. It takes 40 seconds to cook and 6 days to spoil. When consumed, it restores 40 , 37.5 and 15 .\nUsing Twigs as filler will yield Kabobs 50 percent of the time. Mandrake Soup has higher Priority, and will be the result if a Mandrake is used as filler. Similarly, Spicy Chili will be the result if any more Meat is added, and Asparagus Soup will be given if Asparagus is used as filler.\nPrerequisites[edit | edit source]\nRequires:\nRequires:  or\nRequires:\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\nExamples[edit | edit source]\n×3\n×2\n×2\n50% chance to make Kabobs\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nDuring the Pig Fiesta event, Steamed Ham Sandwich takes on a more festive appearance.\nThe Steamed Ham Sandwich is a reference to a scene from an episode of The Simpsons titled \"22 Short Films about Springfield\", where the character Principal Skinner buys hamburgers and calls them steamed hams. The scene has become a popular meme and every examination line for it references it in some way.\nSince Foliage is non-renewable in Hamlet, only a limited number of Steamed Ham Sandwiches can be made without using the Teleportato or a connected Reign of Giants world.\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
