  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Hamlet}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|icon = <gallery>\nSteamed Ham Sandwich.png|Normal\nSteamed Ham Sandwich (Pig Fiesta).png|Pig Fiesta\n</gallery>\n|image = Steamed Ham Sandwich Dropped.png\n|canBeBurned=1\n|foodRecipe = {{Pic|32px|Meat}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Foliage}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Vegetables}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x1<hr>{{Pic|32px|Cooked Meat}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Foliage}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Vegetables}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x1\n|foodType = [[Food Type#Meat|Meat]] {{Pic|32px|Meats|Food Type#Meat}}\n|stack = 40\n|hpRestored = 40\n|hungerRestored = 37.5\n|sanityRestored = 15\n|cooktime = 40 sec\n|priority = 5\n|spoil = 6 days\n|spawnCode = \"steamedhamsandwich\"\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = Science says it's a hamburger.\n|willow = It's a ham sandwich.\n|wolfgang = Is mouthwatering hamburgers.\n|wendy = Old family recipe.\n|wx78 = AN UNFORGETTABLE LUNCHEON\n|wickerbottom = I am prepared for an unforgettable luncheon.\n|woodie = Mouth watering hamburgers.\n|maxwell = They're obviously grilled.\n|wagstaff = Delightfully devilish.\n|wigfrid = 'Tis öbviöusly grilled!\n|webber = These are just hamburgers.\n|walani = It's fast food.\n|warly = Tastes like fast food.\n|woodlegs = 'tis a'unforgettable luncheon.\n|wilba = WILBA THOUGHT SHE WAS'T HAVING STEAMED CLAMS\n|wormwood = Egads!\n|wheeler = I thought I was having steamed clams.\n|choose = maxwell\n}}\nThe '''Steamed Ham Sandwich''' is a [[Crock Pot]] [[Food]] [[Item]] exclusive to the ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC.\n\nIt requires 1 [[Foliage]], 1 [[Meat]] or [[Cooked Meat]], plus a [[Crock Pot#Food values|Vegetable value]] of 1.0 or higher. It takes 40 seconds to cook and 6 days to spoil. When consumed, it restores 40 {{Hp}}, 37.5 {{Hunger}} and 15 {{Sanity}}.\n\nUsing [[Twigs]] as filler will yield [[Kabobs]] 50 percent of the time. [[Mandrake Soup]] has higher [[Crock Pot#Priority|Priority]], and will be the result if a [[Mandrake]] is used as filler. Similarly, [[Spicy Chili]] will be the result if any more [[Meats|Meat]] is added, and [[Asparagus Soup]] will be given if [[Asparagus]] is used as filler.\n__NOTOC__\n== Prerequisites ==\n* Requires: [[File:Foliage.png|link=Foliage]]\n* Requires: [[File:Meat.png|link=Meat]] or [[File:Cooked Meat.png|link=Cooked Meat]]\n* Requires: [[File:Crock Pot Vegetables (no Mandrake).png|link=Vegetables]]\n\n== {{pic|32|Cookbook}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Meat\n|item2 = Foliage\n|item3 = Vegetables\n|item4 = Filler\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Ham Sandwich\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cooked Meat\n|item2 = Foliage\n|item3 = Vegetables\n|item4 = Filler\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Ham Sandwich\n}}\n\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Meat\n|item2 = Foliage\n|item3 = Eggplant\n|item4 = Ice\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Ham Sandwich\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Meat\n|item2 = Foliage\n|count2 = 3\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Ham Sandwich\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Meat\n|item2 = Foliage\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Bean Bugs\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Ham Sandwich\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Meat\n|item2 = Foliage\n|item3 = Aloe\n|item4 = Gummy Slug\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Ham Sandwich\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Meat\n|item2 = Foliage\n|item3 = Corn\n|item4 = Durian\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Ham Sandwich\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cooked Meat\n|item2 = Foliage\n|item3 = Green Cap\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Ham Sandwich\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cooked Meat\n|item2 = Foliage\n|item3 = Corn\n|item4 = Twigs\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Steamed Ham Sandwich\n|note = 50% chance to make [[Kabobs]]\n}}\n\n== {{Pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n[[File:Steamed Ham Sandwich (Pig Fiesta).png|right]]\n* During the [[Pig Fiesta]] event, Steamed Ham Sandwich takes on a more festive appearance.\n* The Steamed Ham Sandwich is a reference to a scene from an episode of ''[[w:c:Simpsons|The Simpsons]]'' titled \"22 Short Films about Springfield\", where the character Principal Skinner buys hamburgers and calls them steamed hams. The scene has become a popular meme and every examination line for it references it in some way.\n*Since Foliage is non-renewable in ''Hamlet'', only a limited number of Steamed Ham Sandwiches can be made without using the [[Wooden Thing|Teleportato]] or a connected ''Reign of Giants'' world.\n\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n[[ru:Ветчина на пару]]\n[[vi:Sandwich Hấp]]\n[[Category:Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]\n[[Category:Healing]]\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]"
